  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A requirement mandates controlled-experiment verification of hemolysis predictions; the supporting validation activity is an observational-study of clinical registry data, which the narrative presents as equivalent but which carries a different activityType, breaking the inference link required by the binding requirement.",
